	* plugins/deinterlace/DI_TomsMoComp/TomsMoComp.h,
	  plugins/deinterlace/DI_MoComp2/MoComp2.h: Don't include malloc.h,
	  makes problems with gcc 4.0 and is obsolete and unneeded anyway.
